title: Aly & Fila - Future Sound of Egypt Collection
description:
Been looking for a collection of every Future Sound of Egypt Episode for a while, unfortunately could only find an incomplete version somewhere. So I decided to put everyting together into one big package myself to do you all a favour :)

Included in this package is:
- FSOE Episodes 1-268 Unsplitted
- FSOE Epsodes 269-303 Splitted and Tagged
- FSOE CD Compilations Volumes 1 and 2

Special thanks to
- Trance_Addict for uploading a whole batch of episodes on kickasstorrents
- Inspiron and AcidTox8 for providing the splitted episodes
- And of course Aly & Fila themselves for providing us with this amazing show for more than 300 episodes. Here's to another 300!
